            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "The Dorsal Patch of Males of the Curaçaoan Long-Nosed bat, Leptonycteris curasoae (Phyllostomidae: Glossophaginae) as a Visual Signal",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Mariana",
