            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Phylogeny of African Myotis Bats (Chiroptera, Vespertilionidae) Inferred from Cytochrome Sequences",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Benoît",
